text: Wander Bra is a 2018 Filipino comedy film written and directed by Joven Tan, starring Kakai Bautista, Myrtle Sarrosa, Gardo Versoza and Gina Pareño. The film was produced by Viva Films and it was released in the Philippines on 12 September 2018. ==Cast== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Viva Films films Category:Philippine films
